Services Agreement
We welcome you to access and use APP, PC client software, websites or other online products and its accompanying products or services and its accompanying products or services (collectively, the Services) as provided by Sahm Capital.
Before accessing or using the Services, please fully read and understand the terms and conditions of this agreement, the Privacy Policy, and any other agreements, terms, rules, announcements, notices and/or other documents provided separately by Sahm Capital which may be applicable to the Services (collectively, the Agreement).  Please pay particular attention to the terms prominently identified in bold in this Agreement.
You confirm that you are eligible to access and use the Services and agree to be bound by the terms and conditions of the Agreement. You further confirm that you have undertaken the requisite due diligence and have full knowledge of the possible risks and agree to undertake all potential risks that may arise from accessing or using the Services and its relevant products.  If you do not agree to the terms and conditions of the Agreement, then the User is not authorized to access or use the Services.
Please note that this Agreement are subject to change periodically without notice and at the sole discretion of Sahm Capital. Any modified or amended terms shall take effect upon the effective date provided in the Agreement or the date of release of such modified or amended terms. Continued access to or use of the Services by you after such amendment or modification of the Agreement constitutes your consent and agreement to abide by such amended or modified terms.
